HEADWORD: Artemia
<hw>Ar*te"mi*a</hw> <pr>(⟦aum⟧r*t⟦ecr⟧"m⟦icr⟧*⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>'A`rtemis</grk>, a Greek
